text: The Rock 'N' Sock Connection was a professional wrestling tag team. The team was made up of The Rock and Mankind. The Rock 'N' Sock Connection are best known for competing in World Wrestling Federation (WWF). During their time as a tag team, they were able to win the WWF Tag Team Championship on three different occasions. == Championships == *World Wrestling Federation **WWF Tag Team Championship (three times) ==References== == Other websites == *The Rock's WWE profile *Mick Foley's WWE profile Category:WWE teams and stables
